Travelers' Choice
TIA Wellness Resort is the new evolution of Asia’s award winning Fusion Maia Da Nang. The resort has been rebranded and upgraded to offer the finest luxury spa experience, alongside cutting-edge, creative wellness programs. Located on the central coast’s pristine My Khe beach and several world heritage sites, TIA accommoda-tion consists solely of private villas, each with their own pool and courtyard garden. More than an escape, it’s an authentic wellness journey featuring all-day breakfast, a Wellness Inclusive stay and service from the heart. Calendar highlights include pop-up art shows and culinary events, rotating weekend retreats and visiting wellness practitioners. Spa and wellness experiences are tailored especially for our guests. The Wellness Inclusive program in-cludes two daily treatments (80minutes in total) from the extensive wellness menu and free daily wellness classes. For those wishing to dive deeper into self-reflection, Retreat Inclusive programs promote relaxa-tion and purposeful living. Guests will enjoy two daily wellness therapies (120 minutes in total) and access to their own personal TIA wellness guide who will tailor the entire journey, including plant-based full-board meals. Our wellness team ensures guests return home with tools to ensure they continue to benefit from their stay after leaving through online resources to support their wellness goals. At TIA we empower guests to play an active role in shaping their reality.
