Kerri L wrote a review Dec 2023
Singapore, Singapore67 contributions43 helpful votes
+1
Wellness Paradise in Danang
I wasn’t sure what to expect but everything about my stay has been wonderful. I am traveling alone for retreat and TIA has exceeded my expectations. It is a boutique resort in Danang with 87 villas all with private pools. The staff are amazing and always available to help with anything you need. Depending on your package you have wellness or retreat treatments each day and if you want additional treatments they are reasonably priced. They have a gym and 2 pools in addition to your private pool. The room is well appointed and is great size for 2 people. Breakfast is included with buffet and Ala Carte of plant based or usual options. The mini bar is refreshed daily with healthy snacks and water. I will definitely be back and bring some friends.
