Imagine a place with a beautiful luxurious villa with your own private pool, which has access to a spa with yoga, breath work, Tai Chi, treatments such as massages or Reike - then imagine this is in DaNang Vietnam, a short ride from Hoi Ann a charming vietnamese town, full of character. Then imagine this place is staffed by the most charming, professional and welcoming staff and you are in TIA Wellness resort Da Nang. How about food? Healthy snacks in the mini bar along with detox water and tea, every day as part of the package - which includes 80 mins per person per day of spa treatments with experts in massage etc. Restaurants and room service (all day and night) offer delicious food with healthy options if you want them - all at reasonable prices. Don't miss the outside…
