5 star Relaxation
We cannot explain in mere words our experience. We booked over a period in August to celebrate our wedding anniversary. The staff were amazing, being always ready to please. The food was brilliant and we defy anyone to say that there wasn’t something on the menu to please and delight. The flexibility of being able to have your breakfast at any time during the day was a refreshing change. The accomodation is first class and the daily supply of snacks and tonic drinks made our stay a pleasure. Access to the beach was easy and day beds/ pool loungers were always available. The town centre of Da Nang was only a cheap taxi ride away and Tia also provide free transport into Hoi An twice a day. Overall we can say that together with 80mins of daily massage, this was the most relaxing…
