Jill L wrote a review Aug 2023
5 contributions
Exceptional luxury spa hotel
This is a beautiful low rise hotel, situated in lovely landscaped gardens, stunning pools and spa and amazing food. You have great privacy in your luxury pool villa with little awareness of neighbouring villas. It feels uncrowded and spacious even when there are many other guests. The food and service are exceptional and a bit different (healthy but varied and high quality) in understated luxurious surroundings. The staff make a point of knowing your individual party and catering to your needs. (Linh in the poolside restaurant took great care to tell us about ingredients and dishes.) The beach is clean and uncrowded though a huge high rise complex being built next door may change that in future. There are views to the downtown buildings further down the beach. There are regular…
