See all nearby attractions.
What are some of the property amenities at TIA Wellness Resort - Spa Inclusive?
Some of the more popular amenities offered include free wifi, free breakfast, and a pool.
See all property amenities.
Which room amenities are available at TIA Wellness Resort - Spa Inclusive?
Top room amenities include a minibar, air conditioning, and a flat screen TV.
See all room amenities.
What food & drink options are available at TIA Wellness Resort - Spa Inclusive?
Guests can enjoy free breakfast, an on-site restaurant, and a lounge during their stay.
Learn more.
Is parking available at TIA Wellness Resort - Spa Inclusive?
Yes, free parking is available to guests.
What are some restaurants close to TIA Wellness Resort - Spa Inclusive?
Conveniently located restaurants include Don Cipriani's, Azure Beach Lounge, and Restaurant Epice.
See all nearby restaurants.
Are there opportunities to exercise at TIA Wellness Resort - Spa Inclusive?
Yes, guests have access to a pool, a fitness center, and a sauna during their stay.
Does TIA Wellness Resort - Spa Inclusive have airport transportation?
Yes, TIA Wellness Resort - Spa Inclusive offers airport transportation for guests. We recommend calling ahead to confirm details.
Are any cleaning services offered at TIA Wellness Resort - Spa Inclusive?
Yes, dry cleaning and laundry service are offered to guests.
Does TIA Wellness Resort - Spa Inclusive offer any business services?
Yes, guests have access to a business center and meeting rooms during their stay.
Which languages are spoken by the staff at TIA Wellness Resort - Spa Inclusive?
The staff speaks multiple languages, including English and Vietnamese.
